Well, as the title says, this is a very basic chat server. It is just 1 file, and has just chatting. No bans, no nicks, nothing. It may be shit quality, but it just may teach some of you newer programmers how Servers can send things they receive to other connected sockets.

Source file is located here -> http://csysonline.net/files/java/ChatServer.java
Class file is located here -> http://csysonline.net/files/java/ChatServer.class
Highly documented source file -> http://csysonline.net/files/java/ChatServer(documented).java

Hope you learn something.

